These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, mexican
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, water-polo
There are 2 different favourite colors: mauve, blue
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
2. the mexican is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Nationality   | mexican    | colombian |
| Sport         | water-polo | skiing    |
| Color     | mauve     | blue      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite
The people have 2 different jobs:  nurse, software-developer
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, train
1. the person driving the train is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the nurse is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | sprite  | mirinda   |
| Job   | software-developer | nurse  |
| Transport     | train   | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, writing
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: metal, trance
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, swimming
1. the person who's hobby is writing is in an even position##4
2. the fan of metal is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Hobby         | collecting   | writing  |
| Music-Genre   | trance | metal  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey   | swimming |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
There 2 different types of food: pomegranate, raspberry
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, superhero
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, thai
1. the argentine is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Food          | pomegranate | raspberry |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero   | fantasy   |
| Nationality     | thai       | argentine      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-5::.
There 2 different types of food: lime, raspberry
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, september
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, skateboard
1. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |
| Food        | lime      | raspberry  |
| Birthday       | september     | june    |
| Transport   | quad-bike | skateboard |

