.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There 2 different types of food: pepper, radish
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, time-travel
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, skiing
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
3. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | radish | pepper     |
| Movie-Genre     | time-travel | documentary |
| Sport   | skiing | sailing    |

 #################################

 
