.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: grey, coral
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, indian
2 different pets are kept: lizard, pony
1. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the colombian is on the left of the indian##1
3. the person who likes grey is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Color         | coral | grey |
| Nationality   | colombian     | indian     |
| Pet           | pony          | lizard     |

